trans-unit.source: Provides flags that determine precompilation behavior.
trans-unit.target: Fornece sinalizadores que determinam o comportamento de pré-compilação.

trans-unit.source: The `PrecompilationFlags` class defines the behavior of the build manager during precompilation.
trans-unit.target: O `PrecompilationFlags` classe define o comportamento do Gestor de compilação durante a pré-compilação da.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager> class takes `PrecompilationFlags` as one of its constructor parameters.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>classe demora `PrecompilationFlags` como um dos respetivos parâmetros do construtor.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>

trans-unit.source: Precompilation can be performed programmatically through <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager> or through the Aspnet_compiler.exe command-line tool.
trans-unit.target: Pré-compilação pode ser executada de forma programática através de <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>ou através da ferramenta de linha de comandos Aspnet_compiler.exe.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Security.AllowPartiallyTrustedCallersAttribute> attribute is generated for the assemblies, which means the assemblies can be called by partially trusted code.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Security.AllowPartiallyTrustedCallersAttribute>atributo é gerado para as assemblagens, que significa que as assemblagens podem ser chamadas pelo código parcialmente fidedigno.</xref:System.Security.AllowPartiallyTrustedCallersAttribute>
